item.description: Dexter Dexter Future coder and investor My name is Dexter and I am 1/3 of team Game of Code. I am a person who is positive about every aspect of life. There are many things I like to do, to see, and to experience. I like to play games, I like to gym, I like to learn new things, I like to hanging out with my friends and I do also like to listen to music.
